patthana16.34:1.1: Ācayagāmiṃ hetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naācayagāmī nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā terasa, ārammaṇe nava …pe… vipāke tīṇi …pe… avigate terasa.
patthana16.34:2.1: Ācayagāmiṃ nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naapacayagāmī nanahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā nava …pe… vipāke tīṇi …pe… avigate nava.
